    <item>
      <title>The Notice Shortcode</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/english/post/notice-shortcode/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 18 Mar 2022 21:47:41 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/english/post/notice-shortcode/</guid>
      
        <description><p>The notice shortcode supports three different types of disclaimers. These are as following:</p>
<h2 id="info-notice">Info Notice</h2>
<pre tabindex="0"><code>{{% notice info %}}
Lorem Impsum..
{{% /notice %}}
</code></pre><div
  class="notice"
>
  <span
    class="notice__title"
  >Info</span><div class="notice__content">
    Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat.
  </div>
</div>

<h2 id="update-notice">Update Notice</h2>
<pre tabindex="0"><code>{{% notice update %}}
Lorem Impsum..
{{% /notice %}}
</code></pre><div
  class="notice
    notice--update
  "
>
  <span
    class="notice__title
      notice__title--update
    "
  >Update</span><div class="notice__content">
    Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat.
  </div>
</div>

<h2 id="warning-notice">Warning Notice</h2>
<pre tabindex="0"><code>{{% notice warning %}}
Lorem Impsum..
{{% /notice %}}
</code></pre><div
  class="notice
    notice--warning
  "
>
  <span
    class="notice__title
      notice__title--warning
    "
  >Warning</span><div class="notice__content">
    Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat.
  </div>
</div></description>
      
